message: Hi Bob! I'm excited to offer you the product for $10000. I believe this is a fair price considering its value. Let me know what you think!

Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate your enthusiasm in this negotiation. Considering my budget, I would like to offer $9000 for the product. I hope we can reach an agreement that works for both of us!
Thanks for your offer, Bob! I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. However, I can go as low as $9500 for the product. I hope we can find common ground!
